Note if you are looking for new content, MCP must be aware of it. If running local MCP, you must run File > Export Local MCP Templates and re-run MCP to pick up the changes. If connected to an Epic backend instead, you will not see them until they are submitted and the build machine exports the latest templates.

Also ensure the backend is at the proper calendar offset to grant the content.

2. For quests, if the quest is on your profile, but the quest is COMPLETE or CLAIMED, verify IsVisibleWhenCompleted or IsVisibleWhenClaimed, respectively, is set on the parent bundle (or the quest if overridden there). The quest will not be allocated otherwise.

Dialogue.3AC06FE64FDC7164DEE735AD234AD24B_DA042F1: (sigh) You know, you could maybe pick up one of these times.
Dialogue.FFAD34FF4D820E79BB6C16BDDD7F6021_DA042F1: And, I'll be honest, even better being your nemesis.
Dialogue.16584A964E635B87214D82B26A29E760_DA042F1: Apparently he really enjoyed being a hostage. He loves attention so that tracks.
Dialogue.592D36F347FF97230FB5C5A694F22F3B_DA042F1: At least, I think that's what he said.
Dialogue.FB0B5FD24AF71A26EC13F8B2D7B7A3DD_DA042F1: But I am sure whatever you're doing is much more important than having a final conversation with your sister.
Dialogue.718FA962415ED7186FACC28746F4FF2C_DA042F1: But I've convinced him to get out of the vengeance game. For now.
Dialogue.8961665B4F30B63F62859E9D98867543_DA042F1: But Pandora's Box is a part of something bigger.
Dialogue.6ED422FC45D341C0CB82AD9E50D763E3_DA042F1: But, if you want the Underground to stay gone, you're going to have to invite them to the table.
Dialogue.FE6384F2421183ABC96B46AB6010F034_DA042F1: But, uh, yeah... I think it's time for me to go.
Dialogue.F0F5DEE040E51CE922BC89A6B0261EEA_DA042F1: Do the right thing this time. I know you will.
Dialogue.B9AA5098489C382DB2C98787C6BEDCA6_DA042F1: Fun times. I'm not really sure what brought that to mind...
Dialogue.59B5E2F24CCFE09B9BD04C8366B8A213_DA042F1: HOPE: Okay that time you definitely sent me to voicemail.
Dialogue.D67E12E94A7E1F7AEF869C968838699B_DA042F1: HOPE: Okay, this time I was really hoping you'd pick up.
Dialogue.6905E7AB4C64C093122CAE9555360AFD_DA042F1: I can see the future through my paintings. So, kind of the same thing.
Dialogue.37174EFD4CA21AD828D071B1D9364963_DA042F1: I can't shake the sense that I'm a part of it too.
Dialogue.446348D6431F9ED5A0FD78B5BDD249D0_DA042F1: I don't know where I'm going or when we'll see each other again.
Dialogue.31DE2F93434951A4A312B7934118B1CC_DA042F1: I don't really know who else I can talk to about this.
Dialogue.06267C674B539AE8ECC724B69FFBE233_DA042F1: I forgot a few things last time.
Dialogue.5E84AB0F4793637DFC25D59ABC1CCD04_DA042F1: I plan on doing that in person.
Dialogue.C947E2B94B6FCA47FC1B449A0E5C1F8D_DA042F1: I set up a meeting. The rest is up to you.
Dialogue.FC1633BD4DAB9BCC24F9CCB5413C45CC_DA042F1: I think I just had to say that.
Dialogue.E792442E4539FDEA08045B9822E934FF_DA042F1: I'm not explaining this well, am I? You know your whole "fire" thing?
Dialogue.3EEF88274E376ED5ACECDBBF62EBA7ED_DA042F1: I'm not leaving this message to gloat. I'm really not.
Dialogue.E9953F174B110067E4B328A9194AAA1D_DA042F1: Jones is still not your biggest fan, what with the nana-napping and all...
Dialogue.1803BFA44D94CA5E45FC39B47AFCC238_DA042F1: Maybe it's you opening Pandora's Box?
Dialogue.5D3F607B41DDD165E24E50AF9E8DBEE4_DA042F1: Remember when I'd accuse you and your friends of trying to ruin the world, and you'd roll your eyes?
Dialogue.3F2A0027475934E1DFCBB9A5F24114B9_DA042F1: So if this is goodbye, it's been nice being your sister.
Dialogue.C9550F61406408D192974C8C30A99109_DA042F1: Take care of yourself. Nisha says "Hi."
Dialogue.6BE9A1674637989794C49DAD977306F8_DA042F1: That's probably it. But I can't rule out another call.
Dialogue.0EE71AB44D8D6165893185B114D29DB1_DA042F1: The Underground are good people. They hate you, so right there you know they've got good judgement.
Dialogue.FC882D624E93E5D76B7C50AFB0DD11D8_DA042F1: Turns out. My art can see the future.
Dialogue.AD683F0A4AE3FC1E7871CAA238EFF075_DA042F1: Well, uh, no, wait, um. I can see the future, but it only shows up in my art.
Dialogue.21A267CB4A32ECA79A921FB083E1B372_DA042F1: With all of your connections you probably know this already...
Dialogue.47B4B9364F05A802173B4A947F6C6460_DA042F1: You are going to feel so bad when you finally listen to these.
Dialogue.709DF71B40414F3D319440964247A91C_DA042F1: You'd say something like "Quiet, the adults are talking."
Dialogue.EA8DDFCD44428957F1793B8CEFBFB685_DA042F1: You're welcome. Don't make a habit of it.
Dialogue.1B81C1DA449EF9CB67241AAD6A65F444_DA042F1: You've got a lot of rebuilding to do. Don't do it alone. Nisha can help.

HabaneroStrings.infopanel_progressionbody3: <b>All players in a team earn and lose the same amount of progress.</>
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_seasonbody1_c4s4: <b>At the start of every season,</> your ranks in Ranked Battle Royale and Ranked Zero Build will reset.
HabaneroStrings.unlockmodal_body2: <b>Complete Ranked Urgent Quests</> to earn unique seasonal rewards.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_habanerobody1: <b>Eliminate opponents</> and <b>place highly</> to progress through the ranks.
HabaneroStrings.unlockmodal_body1: <b>Play a ranked match</> to reveal your rank. Each mode has its own rank.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_seasonbody1: <b>Season Zero is the start of ranked play</> and we may need to make adjustments periodically.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_seasonbody2: At the end of Season Zero <b>your ranked progress will be recorded</> for future reference.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_seasonbody3_c4s4: At the end of each season, your ranked progress will be recorded for future reference.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_tournamentbody3: Check the <b>COMPETE</> tab for upcoming tournaments and eligibility requirements.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_tournamentbody2: Compete to test your skills and earn tournament rewards.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_rewardsbody2_c5s1: Earn a variety of rewards including Sprays, Emoticons, a Pickaxe, and <b>a Backbling that shows off your rank!</>
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_rewardsbody2_c4s4: Earn a variety of rewards including Sprays, Emoticons, and an <b>Back Bling that shows off your rank!</>
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_rewardsbody2: Earn a variety of rewards including Sprays, Emoticons, and an <b>Emote that shows off your rank!</>
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_progressionbody2: Eliminations later in the match are worth more.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_rewardsbody1_c5s1: Every match you can progress towards unlocking unique seasonal rewards in ranked by <b>surviving storm circles during ranked matches.</>
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_rewardsbody1: Every match you'll get a <b>Ranked Urgent Quest.</> Unlock unique seasonal rewards by completing them!
HabaneroStrings.unlockmodal_body3: No new rules to learn. Earn Battle Pass progress as you normally would.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_unrankedhint: Play 1 match to reveal your rank
HabaneroStrings.infomodal_unrankedmessage:
Play one match to 
reveal your rank
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_unrealbody2: Players who achieve this rank cannot be demoted back to Champion during the season.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_progressionbody1: Players who dealt damage to an eliminated player earn a share of the progress.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_matchmakingbody2: The Team Fill option is only available to solo players in ranked modes.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_unrealbody1: The highest rank is Unreal. Upon reaching this rank, <b>players are granted a global leaderboard rank</> which is displayed with their badge.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_tournamentbody1: Unlock access to more tournaments as you rank up.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_matchmakingbody1: While in a party, <b>matchmaking is based on the highest ranked player in the party.</>
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_protectionbody2: With the First Match Loss Protection, your first match <b>will not reduce your Rank progress</> if you perform poorly.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_protectionbody1: You will get a First Match Loss Protection, one for Battle Royale and one for Zero Build, that <b>resets daily at 0:00 UTC.</>
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_habanerobody2: You will have a <b>separate rank</> for Battle Royale and Zero Build.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_seasonbody3: Your final rank in Season Zero will affect your initial rank at the start of the next ranked season.
HabaneroStrings.infopanel_seasonbody2_c4s4: Your final rank in the previous season <b>will affect your initial rank</> at the start of the next season.
